title: Beta Client
body: My beta client just wont run.I press launch and after that nothing appears,but it says that i am already running the client help me {{champion:32}} {{champion:32}} {{champion:32}} {{item:3151}} {{sticker:slayer-pantheon-rainbows}}

replies.body: Can you try running the **LeagueClient.exe** file from inside your installation directory *(C:\Riot Games\League of Legends)* to see if anything changes?
